longBusinessSummary: Lloyds Metals and Energy Limited manufactures and sells sponge iron and iron ore in India. The company operates in four segments: Sponge Iron, Mining, Power, and Pellet. It also offers wire rods and TMT rebars. In addition, the company is involved in the generation of power, and trading of pellets. Lloyds Metals and Energy Limited was incorporated in 1977 and is based in Mumbai, India.
